title: Micah Parsons reveals trade to Eagles was 'very close,' Cowboys wanted Jalen Carter in exchange

sources.name: Yahoo Sports NFL
sources.title: Micah Parsons reveals trade to Eagles was 'very close,' Cowboys wanted Jalen Carter in exchange
sources.description: Dallas wanted to make sure its star pass rusher didn't go to an NFC East rival and included conditions in the trade with the Packers.
